name: Heretic
note:
Dirk's alignment. Has different EXP rates
and slightly different stats, and doesn't
learn skills. Instead, he learns special
abilities at level 1.

The same as chameleon, just with a different
name. Name is switched midway through the 
game.

name: Hacker
note:
Actually Architect, just disguised for the
first portain of the game.

name: Patron
note:
Andrew's version of Patron. None of the
spells are learned, similar to Dirk having
none of Heretic's skills.

name: Keeper
note: Rank's version of Keeper. Similar to Dirk's.

name: Architect
note:
Dasher switches to this alignment near the
end of the game. Exactly the same as the 
fake "Hacker" alignment he had before.
